column2: SELECT TOP #  s.class, s.subclass, count(z.p_el_debiased) AS el_debias, count(z.p_cs_debiased) AS cs_debias, count(zn.p_el) AS el, count(zn.p_cs) AS cs FROM SpecPhotoAll AS s JOIN zooSpec AS z ON S.objID = z.objid JOIN zooNoSpec AS zn ON s.objID = zn.objid WHERE  class <> &&& GROUP BY s.class. s.subclass
